<br />\n感激大家 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請留意各宗「自殺事件」,唔好畀佢哋嘅事沉底呀 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經突破八千字大關<br />\n竟然仲未有黑警被制裁<br />\n我哋每日睇住手足一個一個被清算,一個一個嘅屍體被發現,好多真相慢慢浮面<br />\n但點解佢哋咩事都無?香港法治已死<br />\n我哋已經無辦法回頭<br />\n難道香港人仲要接受垃圾傀儡政府嘅統治?<br />\n香港人應該由香港人管理照顧<br />\n請大家堅持落去<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"c1ad5aa5e0788c111ab566324b3cb5f2a26e99af","tid":1657961,"uid":4151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:31:35.000Z","msg":"多人回post就代表多人？"},{"pid":"7ff57111f41c859fc0543f569520522a4a3c12e8","tid":1657961,"uid":123047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:33:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0155ae705c0fe1c421a2a10db965f2b070c50132","tid":1657961,"uid":76944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:58:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3e481027b1201e51ab7b946164414e9c7a0bd2","tid":1657961,"uid":76944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe2e45aff0e98b4fe8cb1d4bdd88f76b7706f7b","tid":1657961,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:06:21.000Z","msg":"訓左冇睇星期六日前俾連登仔講到失敗到遊行<br />\n最後尾係咪冇人出黎?<br />\n改過個標題,咪撚再放負好冇,激將法冇撚用架"},{"pid":"f22a0bab98b75ec5e6b64837a0e8021807aa363b","tid":1657961,"uid":286785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T16:34:08.000Z","msg":"推"}]}